{"tid":1035661,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"係hall得罪咗個支那妹","createTime":"2019-02-24T17:49:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-24T23:53:22.000Z","uid":174949,"like":1,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"6e6ab3e101f97aca7f433328cf21c259f94c5251","tid":1035661,"uid":174949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T17:49:39.000Z","msg":"之前有個支那妹鍾意我<br />\n一向歧視支那嘅我緊係拒絕啦<br />\n但過咗一個月 佢成日走嚟同我say hi<br />\n有日佢喺我食緊野嗰時坐咗過嚟 問我拎電話<br />\n我答佢我剩係俾我朋友 唔會俾你<br />\n佢問我地係咪朋友<br />\n我答唔係 解埋朋友嘅定義俾佢聽<br />\n之後佢就講我地可能有相同興趣做到朋友<br />\n佢係咁問我野<br />\n我覺得好煩 所以叫佢收聲<br />\n之後我say bye走人<br />\n佢黑撚哂臉<br />\n我一早講咗唔鍾意佢 仲要死纏爛打<br />\n我依家feel到半個hall嘅人見到我都西我臉 特别係支那印度<br />\n我朋友話人地女仔嚟我咁講hurt到人<br />\n但我唔咁做點令佢死心<br />\n雖然好有罪惡感 我唔覺得係我錯"},{"pid":"ef41222a49afcb2ca728769a668536b19a29b270","tid":1035661,"uid":218575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T17:51:14.000Z","msg":"溝個印度妹再聊半個hall嘅人反cup個大陸妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d599a4c496001679cda4ddc464b09728bb33fe2b","tid":1035661,"uid":77895,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T17:52:36.000Z","msg":"學校邊到"},{"pid":"d445c1c9f19f5e72e485ad3a89747d2d5015b5b1","tid":1035661,"uid":174949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d599a4c496001679cda4ddc464b09728bb33fe2b","tid":1035661,"uid":77895,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T17:52:36.000Z","msg":"學校邊到"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T17:55:32.000Z","msg":"加拿大"},{"pid":"eda8bd06354834fe2853a01b0a835c554849c235","tid":1035661,"uid":174949,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"ef41222a49afcb2ca728769a668536b19a29b270","tid":1035661,"uid":218575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T17:51:14.000Z","msg":"溝個印度妹再聊半個hall嘅人反cup個大陸妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T17:58:02.000Z","msg":"印度妹我都歧視 不了<br />\n朋友都無多個 想bully人都難"},{"pid":"ac